. Scale = 0.1 if not otherwise indicated.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption id="DD88D158F3EB3466078C325F04B057C2" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<paragraph id="D19D400C464FF044BB3572FA3FC473D7" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
